    {
      "id": "vXYKeQ3__eoblRFnDbar5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -21.244375649945596,
      "y": 681.6211897626441,
      "width": 570.3995971679688,
      "height": 80,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#868e96",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "al",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1044221440,
      "version": 716,
      "versionNonce": 226103808,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775909556555,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "🤔 剪枝 1 的逻辑是？\nseen 是跟着递归的 nums[idx] 走的，seen.has(buckets[i]) 如果为真，\n那么意味着必然存在一个 j（满足：j < i 且 buckets[j] == buckets[i]）。\nnums[idx] 丢到 buckets[j] 中做了尝试，结果是失败的链路。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🤔 剪枝 1 的逻辑是？\nseen 是跟着递归的 nums[idx] 走的，seen.has(buckets[i]) 如果为真，\n那么意味着必然存在一个 j（满足：j < i 且 buckets[j] == buckets[i]）。\nnums[idx] 丢到 buckets[j] 中做了尝试，结果是失败的链路。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "as1ljz_jyeD153NxTRaqq",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -21.45434564994548,
      "y": 494.3794044118665,
      "width": 594.3998413085938,
      "height": 140,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#868e96",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "am",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2069614080,
      "version": 1223,
      "versionNonce": 745016832,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775909556555,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "🤔 判成功的逻辑是？\nnums 消费完即成功，根本原因在于有仨前提条件兜底：\n1. nums 成员总和是 k 的倍数\n2. nums 所有成员都小于目标值，每个成员都有机会放入桶中\n3. nums 成员入桶的前提是桶不会溢出\n综上，如果 nums 所有成员都被成功分配了，那么各桶的和必然恰好等于 target，\n不存在“所有数字放完了但桶没填满”的情况。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🤔 判成功的逻辑是？\nnums 消费完即成功，根本原因在于有仨前提条件兜底：\n1. nums 成员总和是 k 的倍数\n2. nums 所有成员都小于目标值，每个成员都有机会放入桶中\n3. nums 成员入桶的前提是桶不会溢出\n综上，如果 nums 所有成员都被成功分配了，那么各桶的和必然恰好等于 target，\n不存在“所有数字放完了但桶没填满”的情况。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
